  "title": "Accounts Executive | Full Set | Changi | 5 Days | Up To $3.5K - 4461",
  "description": "<p><strong>Accounts Executive</strong><br />Salary: $3000 - $3500<br />Working Days: Mon – Fri | 9am – 6pm<br />Working Location: Changi Airfreight Centre</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Handle full set of accounts, including AP, AR, GL, and bank reconciliations</li><li>Prepare monthly financial statements, P&L, balance sheet, and cash flow reports</li><li>Maintain accurate accounting records and ensure timely month-end and year-end closing</li><li>Process invoices, credit notes, and journal entries</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum higher LCCI/ACCA or above</li><li>At least 1 year working experience in full set accounting</li><li>Able to start work immediately</li></ul><p><br /><strong>Email: supreme.jacksontan@gmail.com</strong></p><p><strong>Tan Yong Zhi (Jackson) | Reg: R24124461</strong></p><p><strong>The Supreme HR Advisory Pte. Ltd | EA No: 14C7279</strong></p>",
